T12TD4293E:253b-29: nges tshig ldog pa nyid yin no //
T12TD4293E:253b-30: snga na med pa'i bye brag ni //
T12TD4293E:253b-31: rgyun 'dra ba dang rang bzhin dang //
T12TD4293E:253b-32: skabs dang rten la med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:253b-33: rgyun zhig pa dang rang bzhin dang //
T12TD4293E:253b-34: skabs dang rten las bral ba yis //
T12TD4293E:253b-35: zhig nas med pa bzhi yin no //
T12TD4293E:253b-36: phan tshun gcig la gcig med pa //
T12TD4293E:253b-37: mtshan nyid dbye ba yod mod kyi //
T12TD4293E:253b-38: rang bzhin nyid du bsdu bya ste //
T12TD4293E:253b-39: ji ltar gser gyi gdub rgyan dag //
T12TD4293E:253b-40: rigs dang bzo dang bong tshod dang //
T12TD4293E:253b-41: kha dog dbyibs rnams mtshungs mod kyi //
T12TD4293E:253b-42: gcig gi rang bzhin gcig ma yin //
T12TD4293E:253b-43: yin na cig car gzung bar 'gyur //
T12TD4293E:253b-44: shin tu med pa'i bye brag ni //
T12TD4293E:253b-45: rgyu dang rang bzhin gnyis su shes //
T12TD4293E:253b-46: sems can skye ba la sogs pa //
T12TD4293E:253b-47: rgyun dmigs pa yi rang bzhin ni //
T12TD4293E:253b-49: sa bon sa dang 'o ma la //
T12TD4293E:253b-50: myu gu bum pa mar rnams ni //
T12TD4293E:253b-51: rang bzhin snga na med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:253b-52: ji ltar gser las rgyan sogs ni //
T12TD4293E:253b-53: gnas skabs snga na med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:253b-54: sa phyogs 'di na ba lang dag //
T12TD4293E:253b-55: sngon chad med pa rten la'o //
T12TD4293E:253b-56: ljon pa 'am skyes bu la sogs pa //
T12TD4293E:254a-1: gam shi bar gyur pa dag //
T12TD4293E:254a-2: rgyun zhig gyur te med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:254a-3: myu gu bum pa mar rnams la //
T12TD4293E:254a-4: sa bon sa dang 'o ma ni //
T12TD4293E:254a-5: rang bzhin zhig nas med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:254a-6: ji ltar gser gyi gdub rgyan las //
T12TD4293E:254a-7: rna cha dag ni skabs zhig pa //
T12TD4293E:254a-8: sa phyogs 'di nas bum pa dag //
T12TD4293E:254a-9: gzhan du 'phos te med pa ni //
T12TD4293E:254a-10: rten las bral te med pa'o //
T12TD4293E:254a-11: ri bong rnga mo bong bu la //
T12TD4293E:254a-12: rva dang rva yi rgyu med ces //
T12TD4293E:254a-13: rang bzhin dgag dang rgyu dgag pa'o //
T12TD4293E:254a-14: dgag pa dus la ltos pa ni //
T12TD4293E:254a-15: dngos pos dus la ltos pa ste //
T12TD4293E:254a-16: smra ba po yi dus la ni //
T12TD4293E:254a-17: nam yang khong du chud pa 'dzin //
T12TD4293E:254a-18: spyi tsam khong du chud bya dang //
T12TD4293E:254a-19: khyad par khong du chud bya dag //
T12TD4293E:254a-20: smra ba'i bsam pa'ang gnyis su'o //
T12TD4293E:254a-21: ngo bo ston pa ji snyed pa //
T12TD4293E:254a-22: de dag dgag pa'ang de snyed kyi //
T12TD4293E:254a-23: 'on kyang mdo ru bsdu ba ni //
T12TD4293E:254a-24: de dag tsam du shes par bya //
T12TD4293E:254a-25: ldog pa bsdus pa bstan pa'i tshig la 'ur byas pa rdzogs so /
